[section#meta.define.static
    [:en] Promoting to static storage
    [:zh_CN] 提升为静态存储
]

[para]
[:en] The functions in this subclause promote compile-time storage into static storage.
[:zh_CN] 本子条款中的各函数将编译时存储提升为静态存储。

[%@lib reflect_constant_string]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<ranges::[[redoc("`:c>")]]input_range R>
  consteval info reflect_constant_string(R&& r);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`CharT] be [`ranges::range_value_t<R>].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`CharT] 为 [`ranges::range_value_t<R>]。

[para:mandates]
[:en] [`CharT] is a character type ([#basic.fundamental]).
[:zh_CN] [`CharT] 为字符类型（[#basic.fundamental]）。

[para]
[:en] Let [$V] be the pack of values of type [`CharT] whose elements are the
corresponding elements of [`r], except that if [`r] refers to a string literal object,
then [$V] does not include the terminating [=unicode(0000,null)] character of [`r].
[:zh_CN] 令 [$V] 为 [`CharT] 类型的值的包组，其各元素为 [`r] 的对应元素，但当
[`r] 指代字符串字面量对象时，[$V] 不包含 [`r] 的终结 [=unicode(0000,null)] 字符。

[para]
[:en] Let [$P] be the template parameter object ([#temp.param])
of type [`const CharT`[sizeof...(V) + 1`]] initialized with [`{[$V]..., CharT()}].
[:zh_CN] 令 [$P] 为以 [`{[$V]..., CharT()}] 初始化的
[`const CharT`[sizeof...(V) + 1`]] 类型的模板形参对象（[#temp.param]）。

[para:returns]
[:en] [`^^[$P]].
[:zh_CN] [`^^[$P]]。

[para]
[begin:note]
[:en] [$P] is a potentially non-unique object ([#intro.object]).
[:zh_CN] [$P] 是潜在非独有对象（[#intro.object]）。
[end:note]
[div:end]

[%@lib reflect_constant_array]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<ranges::[[redoc("`:c>")]]input_range R>
  consteval info reflect_constant_array(R&& r);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para]
[:en] Let [`U] be [`ranges::range_value_t<R>] and [`T] be [`remove_all_extents_t<U>].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`U] 为 [`ranges::range_value_t<R>]，并令 [`T] 为 [`remove_all_extents_t<U>]。

[para:mandates]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`T] is a structural type ([#temp.param]),
[:zh_CN] [`T] 是结构化类型（[#temp.param]），
[item]
[:en] [`T] satisfies [`:c copy_constructible], and
[:zh_CN] [`T] 符合 [`:c copy_constructible]，以及
[item]
[:en] if [`U] is not an array type, then
[`is_constructible_v<T, ranges::range_reference_t<R>>] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] 若 [`U] 不是数组类型，则
[`is_constructible_v<T, ranges::range_reference_t<R>>] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para]
[:en] Let [$V] be the pack of values of type [`info] of the same size as [`r],
where the [$i^\text{th}] element is
[:zh_CN] 令 [$V] 为大小与 [`r] 相同的 [`info] 类型的值的包组，其中第 [$i] 个元素
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] [`reflect_constant_array(*[$[`[^it]]_i])] if [`U] is an array type,
[:zh_CN@~] 若 [`U] 是数组类型，则为 [`reflect_constant_array(*[$[`[^it]]_i])]，
[item]
[:en@~] [`reflect_constant(static_cast<T>(*[$[`[^it]]_i]))] otherwise,
[:zh_CN@~] 否则为 [`reflect_constant(static_cast<T>(*[$[`[^it]]_i]))]，
[list]
[:en@~] and [$[`[^it]]_i] is an iterator to the [$i^\text{th}] element of [`r].
[:zh_CN@~] 而 [$[`[^it]]_i] 为指向 [`r] 的第 [$i] 个元素的迭代器。

[para]
[:en] Let [$P] be
[:zh_CN] 令 [$P] 为：
[list]
[item]
[:en] the template parameter object ([#temp.param]) of type [`const T`[sizeof...([$V])`]],
such that [`[$P]`[[$I]`]] is template-argument-equivalent ([#temp.type])
to the object represented by [`[$V]...`[[$I]`]] for all [$I] in the range
[=range(0,sizeof...([$V]))] if [`sizeof...([$V]) > 0] is [`true], otherwise
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`sizeof...([$V]) > 0] 为 [`true]，则为 [`const T`[sizeof...([$V])`]]
类型的模板形参对象（[#temp.param]），使得对于范围 [=range(0,sizeof...([$V]))] 中的所有 [$I]，
[`[$P]`[[$I]`]] 按模板实参等价（[#temp.type]）于 [`[$V]...`[[$I]`]] 表示的对象，否则
[item]
[:en] the template parameter object of type [`const array<T, 0>] initialized with [`{}].
[:zh_CN] 为以 [`{}] 初始化的 [`const array<T, 0>] 类型的模板形参对象。
[list:end]

[para:returns]
[:en] [`^^[$P]].
[:zh_CN] [`^^[$P]]。

[para:throws]
[:en] Any of
[:zh_CN] 以下任何之一：
[list]
[item]
[:en@~] an exception thrown by any operation on [`r] or
on iterators and sentinels referring to [`r],
[:zh_CN@~] 在 [`r] 上的或者指代 [`r] 的迭代器和哨位上进行的任何操作所抛出的异常，
[item]
[:en@~] an exception thrown by the evaluation of any argument of
[`reflect_constant] or by any evaluation of [`reflect_constant_array], or
[:zh_CN@~] 由 [`reflect_constant] 的任何实参的求值，或由 [`reflect_constant_array]
的任何求值所抛出的异常，或者
[item]
[:en@~] [`meta::exception] if any invocation of [`reflect_constant]
would exit via an exception.
[:zh_CN@~] 如果 [`reflect_constant] 的任何调用因异常退出，则抛出 [`meta::exception]。
[list:end]

[para]
[begin:note]
[:en] When [`r] is not empty, [$P] is a potentially non-unique object ([#intro.object]).
[:zh_CN] 当 [`r] 非空时，[$P] 是潜在非独有对象（[#intro.object]）。
[end:note]
[div:end]

[%@lib define_static_string]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<ranges::[[redoc("`:c>")]]input_range R>
  consteval const ranges::range_value_t<R>* define_static_string(R&& r);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[codeblock]
return meta::extract<const ranges::range_value_t<R>*>(meta::reflect_constant_string(r));
[codeblock:end]
[div:end]

[%@lib define_static_array]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<ranges::[[redoc("`:c>")]]input_range R>
  consteval span<const ranges::range_value_t<R>, [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]> define_static_array(R&& r);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[codeblock]
using T = ranges::range_value_t<R>;
meta::info array = meta::reflect_constant_array(r);
if (meta::is_array_type(meta::type_of(array))) {
  return span<const T, [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]>(meta::extract<const T*>(array),
                                  meta::extent(meta::type_of(array)));
} else {
  return span<const T, [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]>(static_cast<const T*>(nullptr), 0);
}
[codeblock:end]

[para:remarks]
[:en] If [`ranges::size(r)] is a constant expression,
the second template argument of the returned [`span] type
is [`static_cast<size_t>(ranges::size(r))]; otherwise, it is [`dynamic_extent].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`ranges::size(r)] 是常量表达式，那么所返回的 [`span] 类型的第二个模板实参
为 [`static_cast<size_t>(ranges::size(r))]；否则，为 [`dynamic_extent]。
[div:end]

[%@lib define_static_object]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class T>
  consteval const remove_cvref_t<T>* define_static_object(T&& t);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[codeblock]
using U = remove_cvref_t<T>;
if constexpr (meta::is_class_type(^^U) || meta::is_union_type(^^U)) {
  return addressof(meta::extract<const U&>(
                     meta::reflect_constant(std::forward<T>(t))));
} else if constexpr (meta::is_array_type(^^U)) {
  return addressof(meta::extract<const U&>(
                     meta::reflect_constant_array(std::forward<T>(t))));
} else {
  return define_static_array(span(addressof(t), 1)).data();
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[begin:note]
[:en] For class types, [`define_static_object] provides the address of the template
parameter object ([#temp.param]) that is template-argument equivalent to [`t].
[:zh_CN] 对于类类型，[`define_static_object] 提供的是按模板实参等价于 [`t] 的
模板形参对象（[#temp.param]）的地址。
[end:note]
[div:end]
